name: BIG man
description:
I'm not big. Not above-average big in stature nor status. Not the big man on campus. 
Not big on stats.
That one thing, oh yeah that's big but that's beside the point. Not the Notorious BIG. "It's all good baby baby." 
To be a part of something big- bigger than myself. Well, that's big-time. Bigger than the big apple (corny) bigger than what is able to be accomplished alone.
